  "summary": "authentik: `UserSourceConnection.user` and `GroupSourceConnection.group` are changeable through the API",
  "details": "authentik is an open-source identity provider. Prior to versions 2025.12.6, 2026.2.4, and 2026.5.1, an attacker with the ability to change a source connection, and an account in one of the configured sources can log into any account. This issue has been patched in versions 2025.12.6, 2026.2.4, and 2026.5.1.",
